`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Candidates who do well typically show: a coherent theme across projects, one or two deep dives (e.g., a Kaggle model with error analysis or a hardware prototype with measurements), and clear alignment to a faculty members current work. If you lack formal research experience, emphasize disciplined execution (clean repos, experiment logs) and relevant open-source contributions. For design- or build-heavy labs, attach schematics or videos instead of only GitHub links."}),`
