`,n.jsx(e.h2,{children:"Introduction"}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:'IIT Madras hosts one of Indias most interdisciplinary campuses, blending engineering, data science, sustainability, and deep-tech entrepreneurship through its research park. The summer internship track is prized because interns often work inside active industrial collaborations or translational labs. All dates and stipend cues here are "Expected / Indicative"they mirror 2024/2025 behavior to help you move before announcements land.'}),`
